%20chief%20of%20staff%20for%20policy%20on%20X%2C%20calling%20him%20%26quot%3Banother%20fantastic%20pick%20by%20the%20president.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Miller%20was%20part%20of%20the%20president-elect's%20first%20administration%20and%20served%20as%20his%20senior%20adviser%20and%20director%20of%20speech-writing%20at%20the%20White%20House.%20He%20was%20also%20a%20central%20figure%20behind%20several%20of%20Mr%20Trump's%20policies%20on%20immigration%2C%20including%20the%20Muslim%20travel%20ban%20and%20the%202018%20family%20separation%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMiller's%20Stance%20On%20H-1B%20Visas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20for%20his%20extremist%20rhetoric%2C%20Mr%20Miller%20was%20a%20frequent%20presence%20during%20the%20president-elect's%202024%20campaign%2C%20often%20seen%20speaking%20at%20Mr%20Trump's%20rallies.%20Addressing%20Mr%20Trump's%20infamous%20Madison%20Square%20Garden%20rally%20in%20New%20York%20which%20saw%20an%20attendance%20of%20nearly%2019%2C500%20Americans%2C%20Mr%20Miller%20told%20the%20crowd%20that%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20is%20for%20Americans%20and%20Americans%20only%26quot%3B%20and%20promised%20to%20%26quot%3Brestore%20America%20to%20the%20true%20Americans%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20during%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20Mr%20Miller%20asserted%20that%20if%20Mt%20Trump%20was%20re-elected%2C%20his%20administration%20would%20bring%20policies%20to%20restrict%20legal%20and%20illegal%20immigration.%20He%20also%20talked%20about%20plans%20to%20detain%20undocumented%20immigrants%20in%20camps%20while%20they%20await%20expulsion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Trump's%20first%20administration%2C%20Miller%20helped%20in%20drafting%20the%20Cruz-Sessions%20bill%20that%20prohibited%20international%20students%20with%20a%20master's%20or%20bachelor's%20degree%20from%20working%20in%20H-1B%20status%20in%20the%20US%20for%20at%20least%2010%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20in%20his%20new%20role%20in%20Trump%202.0%2C%20Mr%20Miller%20is%20expected%20to%20continue%20his%20advocacy%20for%20restrictive%20immigration%20policies%2C%20including%20limits%20on%20H-1B%20visas.%20He%20argues%20that%20the%20H-1B%20program%20can%20lead%20to%20American%20worker%20displacement%20and%20wage%20suppression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%20Administration%20And%20Immigration%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20administration's%20stance%20on%20immigration%20has%20often%20been%20at%20odds%20with%20economic%20consensus%2C%20which%20shows%20that%20skilled%20immigrants%20and%20international%20students%20benefit%20the%20US%20economy.%20As%20president%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20did%20not%20enact%20any%20measures%20to%20increase%20access%20to%20H-1B%20visas%2C%20and%20his%20second%20term%20will%20likely%20be%20similar.%20Policies%20introduced%20during%20his%20presidency%20also%20saw%20a%20rise%20in%20visa%20denial%20rates%20and%20a%20narrowing%20of%20the%20definition%20of%20%26quot%3Bspeciality%20occupation%2C%26quot%3B%20reducing%20the%20positions%20eligible%20for%20H-1B%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20before%20Mr%20Trump%20left%20office%2C%20his%20administration%20published%20a%20restrictive%20H-1B%20rule%2C%20which%20was%20blocked%20by%20a%20court%20for%20violating%20the%20Administrative%20Procedure%20Act.%20As%20per%20a%20report%20by%20Forbes%2C%20the%20rule%20included%20numerous%20provisions%20to%20prevent%20companies%20from%20employing%20foreign-born%20scientists%20and%20engineers%2C%20such%20as%20changing%20who%20and%20what%20positions%20could%20qualify%20for%20an%20H-1B%20speciality%20occupation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20his%20previous%20administration's%20agenda%20forward%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20has%20also%20appointed%20former%20acting%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20(ICE)%20director%20Tom%20Homan%20as%20his%20administration's%20%26quot%3BBorder%20Czar.%26quot%3B%20In%20a%20post%20on%20his%20Truth%20Social%20platform%2C%20the%