0postwar%20Iran%20in%20the%201990s%20and%20traveled%20to%20the%20US%20at%20the%20age%20of%2018%20%26quot%3Bon%20the%20promise%20of%20the%20American%20dream%20and%20to%20have%20a%20shot%20at%20a%20better%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20website%20adds%20that%20he%20graduated%20from%20UC%20Berkeley%20with%20a%20double%20major%20and%20Princeton%20with%20a%20Ph.D.%20before%20joining%20McKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20in%20New%20York%20City%20in%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20presidential%20pardon%2C%20his%20website%20states%3A%20%26quot%3BJoy%20at%20the%20outcome.%20Relief%20for%20justice%20at%20last.%20Sadness%20of%20the%20utter%20pain%2C%20distress%2C%20and%20hopelessness%20throughout.%20Exhaustion%20of%20the%20journey.%20And%20ultimately%20thankful%20to%20have%20a%20grave%20weight%20off%20my%20shoulders.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22032f3435-2fc6-4b2b-ad49-f75165f8fbad%5C%22%3EX's%20financial%20issues%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBanki%20is%20joining%20the%20X%20at%20a%20critical%20time%20for%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Musk%20took%20control%20of%20the%20platform%20in%202022%2C%20the%20company%20has%20faced%20financial%20challenges%2C%20including%20a%20drop%20in%20advertising%20revenue.%20Some%20major%20brands%20have%20pulled%20their%20content%20from%20X%2C%20and%20the%20platform%20has%20struggled%20to%20win%20back%20advertisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20September%20report%2C%20market%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-x-advertisers-plan-to-pull-back-spending-survey-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%20firm%20Kantar%20found%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20more%20than%20a%20quarter%20%E2%80%94%20or%2026%25%20%E2%80%94%20of%20advertisers%20surveyed%20planned%20to%20cut%20their%20spending%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20value%20of%20X%20has%20also%20fallen%20sharply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20asset%20manager%20Fidelity%20said%20X%20had%20lost%20over%2071%25%20of%20its%20value%20since%20Musk%20acquired%20it%20in%20October%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported%20in%20August%20that%20Musk's%20Twitter%20purchase%20had%20ended%20up%20being%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-x-twitter-debt-financing-banks-2008-financial-crisis-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworst%20buyout%20financing%20deal%20for%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebanks%20since%20the%202008%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%2413%20billion%20in%20loans%20Musk%20took%20out%20have%20been%20stuck%20on%20banks'%20balance%20sheets%2C%20the%20Journal%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20vision%20for%20X%20also%20includes%20developing%20a%20range%20of%20financial%20features%20that%20could%20allow%20users%20to%20manage%20their%20finances%20entirely%20on%20the%20platform.%20The%20billionaire%20plans%20to%20turn%20X%20into%20an%20%26quot%3Beverything%20app%2C%26quot%3B%20similar%20to%20WeChat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmahmoud-reza-banki-x-cfo-presidential-pardon-donald-trump-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731585470000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6735ddfc192f525898586766%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmahmoud-reza-banki-x-cfo-presidential-pardon-donald-trump-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20X%20has%20tapped%20former%20Tubi%20executive%20Mahmoud%20Reza%20Banki%20as%20the%20platform's%20first%20public%20chief%20financial%20officer%20since%20his%20takeover.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bnolan%40insider.com%20(Beatrice%20Nolan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmahmoud-reza-banki-x-cfo-presidential-pardon-donald-trump-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Muthoot%20Finance%20Q2FY25%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20jumps%2026%25%20to%20Rs%201%2C251%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731585352000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fmuthoot-finance-q2fy25-results-net-profit-jumps-26-to-rs-1-251-crore-124111401268_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Muthoot%20Finance's%20total%20revenue%20from%20operation%20rose%20to%20Rs%204%2C117.4%20crore%20during%20the%20latest%20July-September%20quarter%20from%20Rs%203%2C059.67%20crore%20in%20the%20corresponding%20period%20a%20year%20ago%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fmuthoot-finance-q2fy25-results-net-profit-jumps-26-to-rs-1-251-crore-124111401268_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Trump%20And%20India%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Has%20Enough%20Reason%20To%20Be%20Cautious%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-09%2Fs0ltn3ig_trump-modi-afp_625x300_22_September_19.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20topmost%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20our%20foreign%20policy%20makers%20and%20commentators%20is%20what%20to%20expect%20from%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20second%20term%20as%20regards%20our%20interests.%20Trump's%20unpredictability%20is%20a%20source%20of%20concern%20to%20all%20countries%2C%20whether%20allies%2C%20friends%20or%20adversaries.%20However%2C%20our%20experience%20of%20Trump's%20first%20term%20gives%20us%20confidence%20that%20his%20second%20presidency%20will%20generally%20see%20continuing%20progress%20in%20our%20ties%2C%20the%20foundations%20of%20which%20have%20been%20laid%20in%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20decades%20during%20the%20previous%20Republican%20and%20Democratic%20presidencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20explain%20Indian%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S.%20Jaishankar's%20comment%20that%20some%20countries%20may%20be%20nervous%20about%20Trump%20returning%20to%20power%2C%20but%20India%20is%20not.%20Some%20external%20commentators%20believe%20that%20Trump's%20re-election%20has%20been%20greeted%20with%20enthusiasm%20in%20India%20because%20they%20see%20him%20as%20a%20kindred%20spirit%20of%20Modi%2C%20both%20being%20right-wing%20ideological%20conservatives.%20This%20echoes%20the%20Modi-bashing%20narrative%20promoted%20in%20Western%20progressive%2C%20left-wing%2C%20human%20rights%2C%20minority%20rights%20circles.%20Modi%2C%20no%20doubt%2C%20got%20along%20very%20well%20personally%20with%20Trump%2C%20but%20so%20he%20did%20with%20Biden%2C%20and%2C%20before%20him%2C%20with%20Obama%2C%20too.%20Just%20as%20elements%20of%20the%20policies%20of%20Biden%20and%20Obama%20were%20problematic%20for%20India%2C%20so%20were%20aspects%20of%20Trump's%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERelief%2C%20Not%20Enthusiasm%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20policymaking%20levels%20and%20amongst%20discerning%20commentators%2C%20there%20is%20no%20%26quot%3Benthusiasm%26quot%3B%20as%20such.%20There%20might%20be%20a%20feeling%20of%20some%20relief%20that%20the%20Trump%20administration%20would%20stay%20away%20on%20some%20issues%20on%20which%20the%20Democrats%20have%20harangued%20us.%20On%20these%20issues%2C%20there%20was%20a%20degree%20of%20political%20synergy%20between%20the%20opposition%20in%20India%20and%20Democratic%20circles%2C%20to%20the%20point%20of%20even%20inviting%20US%20interference%20in%20our%20internal%20affairs.%20This%20would%20still%20be%20the%20undercurrent%20in%20India-US%20ties%20as%20the%20Democratic%20ecosystem%20in%20the%20media%2C%20academia%2C%20think%20tanks%2C%20%26quot%3Bprogressive%26quot%3B%20Congressional%20circles%2C%20etc%2C%20will%20remain%20active.%20But%20this%20will%20not%20be%20part%20of%20the%20government%20narrative%20as%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20caveat%20though.%20The%20annual%20reports%20on%20human%20rights%2C%20religious%20freedoms%2C%20etc%2C%20issued%20by%20the%20US%20State%20Department%20are%20mandated%20by%20the%20US%20Congress%2C%20and%20these%20will%20contain%20the%20usual%20salvos%20against%20India.%20One%20can%20expect%20that%20unlike%20Blinken%2C%20who%2C%20unprecedentedly%2C%20singled%20out%20India%20twice%20by%20name%20while%20presenting%20the%20reports%2C%20his%20successor%20is%20unlikely%20to%20do%20so.%20But%20we%20should%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20Christian%20Evangelists%20are%20amongst%20those%20who%20strongly%20support%20Trump%20and%20could%20work%20as%20a%20pressure%20point%20within%20the%20administration%20on%20issues%20relating%20to%20Christian%20%26quot%3Bpersecution%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20conversion%20issue%20and%20restrictions%20on%20NGOs%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20New%20Appointments%20Mean%20For%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20much%20interest%20globally%20in%20the%20appointments%20that%20Trump%20makes%20to%20key%20positions%20in%20his%20administration.%20India%20has%20reason%20to%20be%20satisfied%20with%20his%20nomination%20of%20Marc%20Rubio%20to%20the%20post%20of%20Secretary%20of%20State%20and%20Mike%20Waltz%20as%20the%20National%20Security%20Adviser.%20Rubio%20is%20a%20strong%20supporter%20of%20more%20robust%20defence%2C%20space%20and%20technology%20ties%20with%20India.%20He%20introduced%20the%20US-India%20Defense%20Cooperation%20Act%20in%20the%20Senate%20in%20July%202024%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20bolster%20cooperation%20in%20these%20areas%20with%20India%2C%20besides%20seeking%20exemption%20for%20it%20from%20the%20CAATSA%20(Countering%20America's%20Adversaries%20Through%20Sanctions%20Act)%20legislation%20and%20restricting%20US%20assistance%20to%20Pakistan.%20As%20a%20China%20hawk%2C%20he%20also%20sees%20India%20as%20a%20counterbalance%20to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMike%20Waltz%20is%20the%20Republican%20Co-Chair%20of%20the%20India%20Caucus%2C%20which%20means%20that%20he%20has%20an%20understanding%20of%20India-related%20issues%2C%20has%20been%20receptive%20to%20India's%20concerns%2C%20has%20been%20an%20advocate%20of%20strong%20US-India%20ties%2C%20and%20is%20well-connected%20to%20the%20Indian%20diaspora.%20He%20believes%20that%20the%20US-India%20partnership%20was%20the%20most%20important%20strategic%20relationship%20of%20the%2021st%20century.%20One%20can%20assume%20that%20he%20will%2C%20like%20Jake%20Sullivan%2C%20continue%20to%20lead%20the%20iCET%20(Initiative%20for%20Critical%20and%20Emerging%20Technologies)%20from%20the%20US%20side%2C%20with%20our%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20(NSA)%2C%20Ajit%20Doval%2C%20as%20his%20counterpart.%20This%20is%20important.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20are%20China%20hawks%2C%20which%20means%20that%20the%20Quad%20and%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20Strategy%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20strongly%20backed%20by%20the%20White%20House%20and%20the%20State%20Department.%20Kurt%20Campbell%2C%20earlier%20in%20Biden's%20White%20House%20and%20later%20appointed%20as%20Deputy%20Secretary%20of%20State%20in%20the%20State%20Department%2C%20was%20a%20strong%20proponent%20of%20the%20Quad%20and%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20strategy.%20He%20will%20most%20probably%20leave%20his%20post%2C%20but%20both%20Rubio%20and%20Waltz%20would%20ensure%20that%20this%20part%20of%20the%20India-US%20strategic%20cooperation%2C%20which%20also%20has%20the%20China%20challenge%20in%20view%2C%20continues%20unabated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaution%20Is%20Foremost%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20be%20hosting%20the%20next%20Quad%20summit%20in%202025%2C%20which%20means%20that%20Trump%20should%20be%20coming%20to%20India%20very%20early%20in%20his%20tenure-a%20bonus%20because%20the%20bureaucracies%20in%20both%20countries%20will%20get%20galvanised%20to%20make%20the%20visit%20substantive%20in%20content%20and%20give%20a%20direction%20to%20India-US%20ties%20also%20at%20the%20bilateral%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20be%20cautious%20though%20in%20not%20being%20pushed%2C%20beyond%20a%20certain%20point%2C%20into%20subscribing%20to%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20hawkishness%20on%20China.%20Our%20ties%20with%20Beijing%20will%20remain%20a%20massive%20challenge%20to%20us%20strategically%2C%20even%20if%20there%20has%20been%20some%20positive%20movement%20on%20the%20border%20recently.%20It%20amounts%20to%20some%20lessening%20of%20tensions%20but%20not%20an%20end%20to%20them%2C%20as%20Chinese%20policies%20will%20remain%20unpredictable.%20We%20will%20need%20hedging%20strategies%2C%20for%20which%20the%20Quad%20and%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20strategy%20are%20indispensable.%20We%20need%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20our%20stakes%20in%20BRICS%20and%20the%20Shanghai%20Cooperation%20Organisation%20(SCO)%20as%20part%20of%20maintaining%20a%20balance%20in%20our%20foreign%20policy%20and%20retaining%20some%20cards%20to%20play%20to%20preserve%20our%20strategic%20autonomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%2C%20China%20And%20Russia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20will%20also%20have%20to%20keep%20in%20view%20that%20there%20are%20inherent%20contradictions%20in%20the%20US%20policy%20towards%20China%2C%20and%20Trump's%20approach%20is%20not%20free%20of%20them.%20Trump%20does%20not%20want%20to%20get%20involved%20in%20wars%20abroad%20anymore%2C%20which%20means%20he%20will%20want%20to%20use%20diplomatic%20and%20economic%20tools%20to%20deal%20with%20China's%20expansionism%20and%20its%20threat%20to%20US%20global%20pre-eminence.%20How%20much%20China%20can%20and%20will%20exploit%20this%20contradiction%20to%20continue%20asserting%20itself%20in%20the%20Western%20Pacific%20and%20beyond%2C%20with%20the%20economic%20power%20at%20its%20disposal%20that%20gets%20inevitably%20translated%20into%20political%20influence%2C%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20inclination%20to%20resolve%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%20will%20potentially%20ease%20tensions%2C%20benefiting%20India%20and%20the%20Global%20South.%20Whether%20he%20succeeds%2C%20or%2C%20if%20rebuffed%2C%20ups%20the%20ante%20to%20exert%20more%20pressure%20on%20Russia%2C%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%20If%20a%20direct%20dialogue%20begins%20with%20the%20US%20and%20Russia%2C%20then%20the%20pressure%20on%20Modi%20to%20act%20as%20an%20intermediary%20between%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20and%20find%20some%20common%20ground%20will%20end.%20Zelenskyy's%20latest%20'Victory%20Plan'%20to%20establish%20peace%20will%20also%20become%20redundant.%20Trump%20and%20his%20nominees%20for%20the%20State%20Department%2C%20the%20NSA%20and%20the%20Pentagon%20are%20extremely%20pro-Israel%2C%20and%20this%20does%20not%20bode%20well%20for%20peace%20in%20West%20Asia.%20Trump's%20anti-Iran%20stance%20is%20not%20reassuring%20either%20for%20the%20region%20or%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEconomic%20Pain%20Points%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20economic%20side%2C%20we%20had%20pressure%20from%20Trump%20during%20his%20first%20term%20when%20the%20US%20excluded%20us%20from%20the%20Generalised%20Scheme%20of%20Preferences%20(GSP)%20and%20imposed%20tariffs%20on%20our%20steel%20and%20aluminium%20exports%20to%20the%20US.%20During%20his%20campaign%2C%20he%20has%20referred%20to%20India%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btariff%20king%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20'trade%20abuser'%2C%20even%20as%20he%20has%20spoken%20very%20warmly%20about%20Modi%20personally.%20He%20has%20threatened%20to%20impose%2060%25%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20exports%20to%20the%20US%20and%2010-20%25%20tariffs%20on%20imports%20from%20other%20countries.%20Many%20in%20Indian%20economic%20circles%20believe%20that%20we%20could%20handle%20a%2010%25%20tariff%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20and%20with%20much%20higher%20import%20duties%20on%20China%2C%20we%20could%20even%20benefit%20in%20some%20areas.%20There%20is%20concern%20that%20Trump%20might%20tighten%20up%20on%20H1B%20visas%2C%20the%20stronger%20controls%20on%20technology%20transfers%20from%20the%20US%20might%20affect%20us%20too%2C%20and%20Trump's%20determination%20to%20push%20American%20corporations%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20US%20and%20create%20jobs%20there%20might%20alter%20the%20discourse%20on%20friend-shoring%20or%20resilient%20supply%20chains%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nomination%20of%20Robert%20Lighthiser%2C%20the%20US%20Trade%20Representative%20in%20Trump's%20first%20term%20and%20someone%20India%20found%20difficult%20to%20deal%20with%2C%20to%20define%20US%20trade%20policy%20in%20the%20president's%20second%20term%20will%20be%20problematic%20all%20around.%20He%20is%20truly%20a%20trade%20hawk%20who%20wants%20to%20use%20US%20economic%20power%20aggressively%20to%20protect%20the%20country's%20interests%20as%20he%20perceives%20them%2C%20to%20the%20point%20of%20wrecking%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organization%20(WTO)%2C%20if%20he%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECounting%20On%20Modi-Trump%20Rapport%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20the%20advantage%2C%20even%20with%20these%20difficulties%2C%20of%20a%20personal%20rapport%20between%20Modi%20and%20Trump%20and%20political%20backing%20prospectively%20in%20the%20State%20Department%20and%20at%20the%20level%20of%20the%20National%20Security%20Advisor%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20in%20the%20US%20Congress%2C%20to%20counter%20undue%20trade%20pressures.%20Even%20on%20the%20US%20side%2C%20they%20will%20have%20to%20take%20the%20totality%20of%20US%20long-term%20interests%20in%20India%20to%20fashion%20a%20balanced%20policy%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20we%20can%20hope%20that%20the%20approach%20of%20the%20Biden%20administration%20on%20the%20Nijjar%20and%20Pannun%20affairs%20will%20become%20more%20discreet%20rather%20than%20one%20that%20resorts%20to%20unquestioningly%20supporting%20Trudeau%2C%20talking%20down%20at%20India%20by%20demanding%20satisfaction%20and%20accountability%2C%20and%20giving%20free%20rein%20to%20Pannun%20to%20threaten%20India%20with%20terrorism%2C%20death%20threats%2C%20etc.%20Trump%20has%20called%20Trudeau%20'weak'%2C%20'dishonest'%20and%20'two-faced'.%20That%20holds%20out%20some%20hope%20that%20Trudeau%20will%20become%20less%20provocative.%20One%20must%20keep%20in%20mind%20though%20that%20as%20the%20Pannun%20case%20is%20before%20courts%2C%20information%20on%20the%20proceedings%20will%20make%20news%20that%20anti-Indian%20elements%20abroad%20will%20pick%20up%20and%20which%20our%20press%20will%20play%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInteresting%20times%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Kanwal%20Sibal%20was%20Foreign%20Secretary%20and%20Ambassador%20to%20Turkey%2C%20Egypt%2C%20France%20and%20Russia%2C%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Of%20Mission%20in%20Washington.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731585180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-09%2Fs0ltn3ig_trump-modi-afp_625x300_22_September_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdonald-trump-and-india-new-delhi-has-enough-reason-to-be-careful-7018567%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20need%20to%20be%20cautious%20in%20not%20being%20pushed%2C%20beyond%20a%20certain%20point%2C%20into%20subscribing%20to%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20hawkishness%20on%20China.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdonald-trump-and-india-new-delhi-has-enough-reason-to-be-careful-7018567%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Crompton%20Greaves%20Q2FY25%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20rises%2027%25%20to%20Rs%20128%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731585148000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fcrompton-greaves-q2fy25-results-net-profit-