2%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-financial-safety-net-money-independence-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AFSPA%20Imposed%20In%20New%20Areas%20Of%20Manipur%20Amid%20Fresh%20Violence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20reimposed%20a%20law%20to%20protect%20security%20forces%20in%20hostile%20areas%20in%20several%20new%20locations%20in%20ethnic%20violence-hit%20Manipur.%20The%20Armed%20Forces%20(Special%20Powers)%20Act%20has%20been%20reimposed%20in%20six%20police%20station%20areas%20including%20Jiribam%2C%20where%2010%20suspected%20Kuki%20militants%20were%20shot%20dead%20in%20an%20encounter%20with%20the%20security%20forces%20on%20Monday%2C%20and%20from%20where%20three%20women%20and%20three%20children%20of%20the%20Meitei%20community%20were%20kidnapped%20by%20suspected%20insurgents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AFSPA%20gives%20sweeping%20powers%20to%20the%20military%20to%20operate%20freely%20anywhere%20that%20has%20been%20declared%20a%20%26quot%3Bdisturbed%20area%26quot%3B%3B%20no%20military%20personnel%20in%20an%20area%20where%20AFSPA%20is%20in%20force%20can%20be%20prosecuted%20without%20the%20Centre's%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%2C%2019%20police%20station%20areas%20in%20Manipur%20were%20not%20under%20AFSPA%20coverage%20as%20they%20were%20considered%20peaceful.%20The%20recent%20escalation%20in%20violence%2C%20however%2C%20has%20brought%20the%20controversial%20law%20back%20to%20at%20least%20six%20police%20station%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20areas%20where%20the%20security%20forces%20can%20operate%20under%20the%20immunity%20provided%20by%20AFSPA%20in%20Manipur%20are%20Sekmai%20and%20Lamsang%20in%20Imphal%20West%20district%2C%20Lamlai%20in%20Imphal%20East%20district%2C%20Jiribam%20in%20Jiribam%20district%2C%20Leimakhong%20in%20Kangpokpi%2C%20and%20Moirang%20in%20Bishnupur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAFSPA%20was%20withdrawn%20from%2019%20police%20station%20areas%20in%20the%20valley%20region%20after%20seeing%20normalcy.%20The%20Meitei-Kuki%20ethnic%20violence%20that%20broke%20out%20in%20May%202023%2C%20however%2C%20led%20to%20many%20young%20people%20taking%20up%20arms.%20Meitei%20insurgent%20groups%20that%20had%20been%20active%20only%20in%20Myanmar%20after%20being%20pushed%20out%20of%20India%20have%20allegedly%20returned%20to%20the%20valley%20in%20large%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki-Zo%20tribes%20also%20have%20nearly%2024%20insurgent%20groups%20that%20have%20signed%20a%20ceasefire%20with%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20state%20government%2C%20called%20the%20Suspension%20of%20Operations%20(SoO)%20agreement.%20The%20agreement%20says%20the%20insurgents%20are%20to%20stay%20in%20designated%20camps%20and%20their%20weapons%20kept%20in%20locked%20storage%2C%20to%20be%20monitored%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20insurgent%20groups%2C%20too%2C%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20training%20young%20people%20and%20supplying%20weapons%20to%20fight%20Meitei%20groups%2C%20especially%20the%20armed%20group%20Arambai%20Tenggol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20armed%20groups%20that%20sprang%20up%20after%20May%202023%20call%20themselves%20%26quot%3Bvillage%20defence%20volunteers%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731582120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Frkfkcieo_manipur-generic_625x300_23_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-imposes-afspa-in-some-new-areas-of-manipur-amid-fresh-incidents-of-violence-7018045%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Centre%20has%20reimposed%20a%20law%20to%20protect%20security%20forces%20in%20hostile%20areas%20AFSPA%20in%20several%20new%20locations%20in%20ethnic%20violence-hit%20Manipur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-imposes-afspa-in-some-new-areas-of-manipur-amid-fresh-incidents-of-viole