in.%20And%20the%20leopard%20jumped%20and%20went%20all%20in%2C%20without%20worrying%20about%20her%20own%20life.%20The%20fierce%20leopard%20kicked%20the%20lioness%20and%20made%20her%20jump%20back%2C%20holding%20her%20paw%20like%20an%20injured%20puppy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cubs%20used%20this%20time%20to%20hide.%20When%20the%20lioness%20jumped%20back%2C%20the%20leopard%20too%20escaped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20leopard%20had%20to%20move%20her%20cubs%20twice%20that%20afternoon.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20did%20seem%20to%20be%20exhausted%20but%20was%20left%20with%20only%20minor%20injuries.%20As%20for%20the%20lioness%2C%20she%20was%20left%20with%20a%20very%20sore%20leg.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731580380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fhpkjhj8g_leopard-fights-lion-to-save-cubs_625x300_14_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvideo-mother-leopard-fights-a-lion-head-on-saves-2-cubs-in-africa-7017746%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20remarkable%20display%20of%20motherly%20love%20and%20courage%2C%20a%20video%20is%20doing%20rounds%20of%20the%20internet%20in%20which%20a%20mother%20leopard%20is%20seen%20fighting%20a%20lion%20head-on%2C%20to%20save%20her%20two%20cubs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvideo-mother-leopard-fights-a-lion-head-on-saves-2-cubs-in-africa-7017746%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22COP29%20host%20Azerbaijan%20says%20doors%20'still%20open'%20after%20spat%20with%20France%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731580359000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115296554%2Cimgsize-2025825.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fcop29-host-azerbaijan-says-doors-still-open-after-spat-with-france%2Farticleshow%2F115295780.cms%